<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_BuildMode_CameraControls" s="314889">
  <T n="name">0xABF062A2<!--String: "Camera Controls"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_CameraControlsLiveBB_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:6d6e43c037ab4057</T>
      <T n="text">0xC82DC18<!--String: "The game has two different <b><font color='#199C2C'>Camera Styles</font></b>; the default <b><font color='#199C2C'>Sims 4 Camera</font></b>, and the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Sims 3 Camera</font></b>. \n\nYou can change the Camera Style in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Camera Controls menu</font></b>, or the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Game Camera</font></b> section of the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Game Options</font></b> (in the latter, you can also invert the camera rotation)."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_CameraControlsLiveBB_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:6d6e43c037ab4054</T>
      <T n="text">0x3713A345<!--String: "To <b><font color='#199C2C'>pan</font></b> (move around) the camera, hold the scroll wheel (TS4 Camera) or the right mouse button (TS3 Camera) and move the mouse, or use the arrows or [W], [A], [S], and [D] keys on the keyboard.\n\nTo <b><font color='#199C2C'>rotate</font></b> the camera, hold the right mouse button (TS4 Camera) or the scroll wheel (TS3 camera) and move the mouse. You can only tilt the camera vertically with the Sims 3 Camera Style.\n\n<b><font color='#199C2C'>Zoom in and out</font></b> using the mouse scroll wheel or the [+] and [-] keys on the keyboard."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_CameraControlsLiveBB_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:6d6e43c037ab4055</T>
      <T n="text">0x230F45D0<!--String: "To <b><font color='#199C2C'>move between floors</font></b>, use the Go Up to Next Floor and Go Down to Lower Floor buttons, or use the [Page Up] and [Page Down] keys on the keyboard.\n\nTo <b><font color='#199C2C'>hide or show the walls</font></b>, use the Walls View button or the [Home] and [End] keys on the keyboard to rotate between the settings."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_CameraControls_BuildOnly_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:bb43048e335a7eab</T>
      <T n="text">0x615CF3F1<!--String: "In <b><font color='#199C2C'>Build Mode</font></b> there’s a <b><font color='#199C2C'>top-down Camera angle</font></b> you can toggle with the Top Down View button or the [T] key on the keyboard."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
